    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Fuinjutsu </p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 5 (Spell Level 3)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 18 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 6 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 18</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> C, H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You touch a creature and apply a seal that prevents it from using any technique that ends its own life, such as Jisatsu no Jutsu or Bakuretsu Junjiru no Jutsu, and grants the subject a +2 bonus to saves against poisons and diseases.</p>\n\n\n\n",
